+# connie-lang
+
+Configuration language for [connie](https://github.com/mattinsler/connie).
+
+## Installation
+
+```bash
+$ npm install --save connie-lang
+```
+
+## Usage
+
+```javascript
+var ConnieLang = require('connie-lang');
+
+var config = ConnieLang.parse({
+  common: {
+    domain: 'mattinsler.com'
+  },
+  endpoints: {
+    api: 'api.@{common.domain}'
+  },
+  server: {
+    port: '#{${PORT} || 3000}'
+  }
+}, process.env);
+
+```
